			<h3 ><a href="#p113422">Re: Dead Neato XV-11, and horrible customer service</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=113422&amp;sid=f768cd779c2d1aba9024bea60f9669bf#p113422"><img src="./styles/robotreviews/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1074&amp;sid=f768cd779c2d1aba9024bea60f9669bf">vic7767</a></strong> &raquo; January 22nd, 2013, 8:29 pm </p>

			

